OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FA patient who was tested for the
OL,7,Fsuspected Ebola virus at a Glasgow
OL,8,Fhospital has tested negative.
OL,10,FIt is understood the patient was
OL,11,Fadmitted to the Queen Elizabeth
OL,12,FUniversity Hospital in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Tuesday, with part of the site
OL,14,Fclosed during testing.
OL,16,FPublic Health Scotland (PHS) said it
OL,17,Fwas aware that an individual in
OL,18,FScotland was tested for Ebola as a
OL,19,Fprecautionary measure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
