FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FConfirming that a result has now been
OL,7,Freceived and is negative, a PHS
OL,8,Fspokesperson said there are "no
OL,9,Fconfirmed cases of Ebola" in Scotland
OL,10,Fright now.
OL,12,F"Public Health Scotland is working
OL,13,Fclosely with UKHSA to assess routes by
OL,14,Fwhich travellers may enter the UK from
OL,15,Faffected countries," they continued.
OL,17,F"The risk from people arriving in the
OL,18,FUK from affected areas is low and the
OL,19,FNHS has safe procedures in place for
OL,20,Fdetecting and managing any such cases.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@YO]tD@AOUwD@TO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
