OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,F"PHS and NHS boards across Scotland
OL,7,Fhave well-established protocols for
OL,8,Fassessing and testing travellers
OL,9,Farriving in the UK from areas affected
OL,10,Fby Ebola where necessary.
OL,12,F"Where required, contact tracing will
OL,13,Foccur and contacts may undergo
OL,14,Fclinical assessment and precautionary
OL,15,Ftesting."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
