CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FThe UK has committed up to #21 million
OL,7,Fto support the local response to Ebola
OL,8,Fin DRC, helping to protect frontline
OL,9,Fworkers and vulnerable communities.
OL,11,FOfficials have stressed that diseases
OL,12,F"are not restricted by borders" and it
OL,13,Fis "vital" the UK works with
OL,14,Finternational partners to protect
OL,15,Fglobal health.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@_O]uD@DOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
