PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FThe experts from the UK Public Health
OL,7,FRapid Support Team include seven
OL,8,Fspecialists from the UK Health
OL,9,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) and the London
OL,10,FSchool of Hygiene and Tropical
OL,11,FMedicine.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
