PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FFour are to be based in the eastern
OL,7,FDRC to support World Health
OL,8,FOrganisation (WHO) field operations,
OL,9,Fwhile one will join the WHO country
OL,10,Foffice in the capital Kinshasa.
OL,12,FAn epidemiologist will also be sent to
OL,13,Fthe Republic of Congo to support the
OL,14,Fwider response in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
