PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,FDr Edmund Newman, director of the UK
OL,7,FPublic Health Rapid Support Team at
OL,8,FUKHSA, said: "This deployment will
OL,9,Fhelp strengthen the existing response
OL,10,Fto the Ebola outbreak in the DRC and
OL,11,Facross the region, with experts in
OL,12,Fepidemiology, risk communications and
OL,13,Fcommunity engagement, infection
OL,14,Fprevention and control and data
OL,15,Fmodelling now on the ground to support.
OL,26,@pD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
