PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782902882
OL,3,CPatient tests negative for Ebola after
OL,4,Csuspected case at Glasgow hospital
OL,6,F"We know infectious diseases are not
OL,7,Frestricted by borders, which is why
OL,8,Fit's vital we continue to work
OL,9,Fcollaboratively with the World Health
OL,10,FOrganisation and other international
OL,11,Fpartners, as well as national and
OL,12,Flocal response organisations, to
OL,13,Fprotect global health security."
OL,15,FA UK Public Health Rapid Support Team
OL,16,Fwas developed during the West Africa
OL,17,FEbola outbreak in 2014/15.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@`O]
